                    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="images/026.gif" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<span id="Label1" style="color:Red;font-weight:bold;width:120px;">学生作品</span></td>
                    <td background="images/rtb2.jpg" width="627" height="38"><table width="95%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" height="19"><tr><td style="height: 19px" width="100%" align="center"><span id="lbtitle" style="color:Black;font-size:Large;font-weight:bold;">聚焦正能量，实现中国梦</span></td></tr></table></td></tr>
